	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			        &nbsp; Level Select - 					
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the Load/Save menu hold R1 and press Up, Down, Square, Up, Down, Square, Up, Down, Square, Down, Up, X</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Unlock all in-game Videos - At the Main Menu first highlight the second choice and then enter the following code -				
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">L1, Left, Right, Square, Triangle, Circle</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Activate the Secret Missions - 					
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">In order to achive this simply highlight any mission that has a shuriken(Throwing star) beside it. Now press and hold "SELECT" while choosing the mission</font>&nbsp;<br>
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
